HOUSE BILL 2048
By McCalmon
SENATE BILL 2426
By Crowe
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 49,
relative to pre-kindergarten.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 49-6-108, is amended by deleting
subdivision (6) and substituting:
(6) Provide an annual report by July 1 of each year to the governor and the
general assembly on the status of pre-kindergarten programs that includes, at a
minimum, the number, location, and types of providers of pre-kindergarten classrooms
and the number of at-risk children served. The department of education, office of early
learning shall publish the report on its website to provide public access to the report.
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
